<D>__{that's probably what they thought when they built me. but my brain is cyber organic patterned after the human brain it functions the same way a human brain does. it accumulates random images and sensations during waking hours, but unlike the human brain that sloughs them off during sleep }
<C>__{ripley}
<D>__{androids don't sleep.}
